page.title: 01GAZETTEER
page.content: Our block is mostly farmland.The crops are mainly wheat.There is lots of rough grazing.The area is very undulated and is very highly cultivated,or it is residential.Our block has two military sites.We call the land around us chalk downland because it is very chalky.The average level of the land above the sea is 74 metres.One residential area is Littleton and its grid reference number is 04450132.Worthy Down's grid reference number is 04470134.The Flowerdown grid reference number is 04460132.There is easy access to one of the main S/N trunk roads.Apart from the three residential areas we have talked about the rest of our block is sparsely populated.
